---
/**
 * SafetySignals Component
 * Single Responsibility: Explain how we evaluate casino safety and handle complaints
 */
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800" id="safety-signals">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">🛡️ Safety & Complaint Awareness</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          How we evaluate casino safety and why complaint history matters in our ratings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Safety Evaluation -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mr-3">✅</span>
            What We Check
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 mr-3 mt-1">🔐</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Valid Licensing</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">MGA, UKGC, Curaçao, Kahnawake - verified jurisdictions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 mr-3 mt-1">🎲</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">RNG Certification</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Games tested by eCOGRA, iTech Labs, or GLI</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 mr-3 mt-1">📄</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Clear Terms</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Transparent bonus T&Cs, withdrawal policies, and limits</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 mr-3 mt-1">🔒</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">SSL Encryption</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Bank-level security for all transactions</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 mr-3 mt-1">👥</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Ownership History</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Years in operation and parent company reputation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Complaint Consideration -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mr-3">⚖️</span>
            Complaint Signals
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              We consider complaint patterns when evaluating casinos, though we don't operate a complaint center ourselves.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-yellow-400 mr-3 mt-1">📊</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Complaint Ratio</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Number of complaints relative to player base size</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-yellow-400 mr-3 mt-1">✔️</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Resolution Rate</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">How many disputes are resolved fairly</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-yellow-400 mr-3 mt-1">⏱️</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Response Time</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">How quickly casinos address player issues</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-yellow-400 mr-3 mt-1">🔍</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Issue Patterns</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Common problem types (payment delays, bonus disputes, etc.)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Rating Impact -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/50 to-purple-900/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-500/30">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="text-4xl mr-4">🎯</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">How This Affects Our Ratings</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
                  <strong class="text-white">Security & Fairness (20%):</strong> Valid licenses, RNG certification, terms transparency
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">
                  <strong class="text-white">Reputation Signals (10%):</strong> Complaint ratios, resolution rates, industry standing
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-600">
              <a href="/guides/how-we-rate" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-semibold inline-flex items-center">
                Read Our Full Rating Methodology
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust Badges -->
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">Casinos we recommend must meet these standards:</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <span class="bg-green-900/30 border border-green-500/30 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ✓ Licensed & Regulated
          </span>
          <span class="bg-green-900/30 border border-green-500/30 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ✓ RNG Certified
          </span>
          <span class="bg-green-900/30 border border-green-500/30 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ✓ Fair T&Cs
          </span>
          <span class="bg-green-900/30 border border-green-500/30 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ✓ Secure Payments
          </span>
          <span class="bg-green-900/30 border border-green-500/30 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ✓ Responsive Support
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
